column6: The Vapers Ph is a community page for the Philippine vaping community. Like and follow us here and on Twitter @thevapersph if you're interested in being a member and being part of the new vaping revolution!
column31: Officials Who Act as Conduits for Foreign Vested Interest Groups Should be Fired – Solon Government officials who serve as conduits for foreign vested interest groups trying to influence local policies should be fired, Ako Bicol Rep. Alfredo A. Garbin Jr. said in a statement issued on Sunday. “While I commend foreign private institutions that support government initiatives, I condemn moves to hijack government policy decisions,” Garbin said. Read more: https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1406916/officials-who-act-as-conduits-for-foreign-vested-interest-groups-should-be-fired-solon#ixzz6pFwMXB6Q Photo Source: https://www.facebook.com/congpido/photos/761507021390693 #TheVapersPH #VapeResponsibly
